  "body": "the current `permit` implementation does not correctly validate signatures. It relies on `_approve` implementation details to cover up the incomplete validation. Anyone copy+pasting the implementation or overriding the `_approve` function will accidentally allow `permit`s with invalid signatures\r\n\r\nrecommendation:\r\nadd a `recoveredSig != address(0)` check to the permit function. Accept that this is redundant",
